title: High-profile financial leader to speak at Nottingham (The University of Nottingham)
text: ( Source : The University of Nottingham ) PA 166 /15 The School of Economics at The University of Nottingham will be welcoming Robert Chote , the Chair of the Office for Budget Responsibility , as a guest lecturer on Thursday 22 October .
